<h1 id="introduction">Introduction</h1>

<p><a href="https://ohmybash.github.io/">Oh-My-Bash</a> is a styling set for your terminal and open source to manage your settings in BASH. It comes with a ton of useful functions, help, plugins, themes and more! If youâ€™ve heard about <a href="https://ohmyz.sh/">Oh-My-Zsh</a> before, this project is a fork of it, but in <a href="https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/">Bourne Again Shell</a>.</p>

